title: Problem receiving email
buttons: conclude: Yes, problememailticket: No

<p>Usually this is because your email software is having a problem that can be resolved by restarting your software or rebooting your computer. Let's try restarting your email software first. If that doesn't work, try rebooting your computer.</p>

<p class="dont-say">Wait for them to restart their software or computer.</p>

<p>Did that fix the problem?</p>
